Package com.abdcelik

Class SkipList<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>

java.lang.Object
com.abdcelik.SkipList<E>
Type Parameters:
E - type of element to be stored
public class SkipList<E extends java.lang.Comparable<E>>
extends java.lang.Object
Each node in the lowest-level list keeps several elements instead of just one element as in a B-tree node.
